package cn.himpqblog.slience.hook

/*
 * Rename this file to Hook.kt after you have a valid libxposed API artifact
 * in mavenLocal() and have enabled:
 *
 *   enableModernLsposed=true
 *
 * Recommended compatibility strategy for API 100 and 101:
 * - module.prop:
 *     minApiVersion=100
 *     targetApiVersion=101
 * - Only use the common subset that exists in both.
 * - Do not depend on helper/service unless you also provide those artifacts.
 * - Avoid API-101-only conveniences until you confirm them in the exact jar.
 *
 * Read:
 * https://github.com/LSPosed/LSPosed/wiki/Develop-Xposed-Modules-Using-Modern-Xposed-API
 */
